{"tid":2310280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美專家：台灣8艘潛艦可炸掉1支共軍艦隊","createTime":"2020-12-03T06:45:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T15:23:52.000Z","uid":184679,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"8a6fa7dfa314efbc959374b9188ffe406a2cb379","tid":2310280,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T06:45:48.000Z","msg":"台灣潛艦國造計畫日前已經啟動，美國知名軍事記者大衛．艾克斯（David Axe）對此表示，台灣單靠預計建造的8艘潛艦，就能摧毀1支中國的入侵艦隊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/WxxOSXXZjimXLGs_2gnbKg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM2MC4zNjkyMzA3NjkyMzA4/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/Ufb50r8J3QFgzvjFwqit_A--~B/aD0zNjY7dz02NTA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/setn.com.tw/8a2663830e6313258971de5397bfa4d6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FWxxOSXXZjimXLGs_2gnbKg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM2MC4zNjkyMzA3NjkyMzA4%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FUfb50r8J3QFgzvjFwqit_A--~B%2FaD0zNjY7dz02NTA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F8a2663830e6313258971de5397bfa4d6&h=7c21e459&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n艾克斯在《富比士》（Forbes，又譯為富比世）刊文指出，台灣預計打造的8艘潛艦，可能總共需要耗資160億美元（約台幣4559億元），不過每一分錢都相當值得，艾克斯引述美國維吉尼亞州智庫「2049計畫研究所」執行董事馬克&middot;斯托克斯（Mark Stokes）所說：「價值不可低估。」<br />\n<br />\n艾克斯認為，台灣海軍欲透過這些新的潛艇，攻擊載有入侵部隊的中國軍艦，而美國麻省理工學院（MIT）的潛艦專家歐文．柯特（Owen Cote）指出，世界上許多海軍的海上、空中反潛能力極差，中國艦隊難以事先發現台灣潛艦，原因是相較於反潛戰部隊，台灣海峽的潛水區非常有利於潛艦行動，而比較雙方的潛艦數量是沒有意義的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8IGGacrtj9i42jULNj4YrQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM2MC4zNjkyMzA3NjkyMzA4/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/setn.com.tw/4d4d9fa731484fa6a545917e1ac08127\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F8IGGacrtj9i42jULNj4YrQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM2MC4zNjkyMzA3NjkyMzA4%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F4d4d9fa731484fa6a545917e1ac08127&h=d39b8994&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n艾克斯指出，中國海軍擁有大約70艘攻擊潛艦，外加數十架配備聲納的水面戰艦和海上巡邏機，但這些部隊將無法突破一小群台灣潛艦，這就是為何台灣的潛艦國造計畫意義重大，台灣國造潛艦預計配備馬克48魚雷和魚叉反艦飛彈，這些新血將極大地加強台灣的防禦能力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/習近平小心-他-台灣8艘炸爛1艦隊-015516869.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E5%B0%8F%E5%BF%83-%E4%BB%96-%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A38%E8%89%98%E7%82%B8%E7%88%9B1%E8%89%A6%E9%9A%8A-015516869.html&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPTsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=8dd35dec\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/習近平小心-他-台灣8艘炸爛1艦隊-015516869.html</a>"},{"pid":"0efdd9e3fc46a7d48322169a2b7a4f2da1f14197","tid":2310280,"uid":55913,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T08:07:37.000Z","msg":"夠打既一早打左搶埋啦洗撚咀炮咩<br />\n你睇香港又打又殺幾威威"},{"pid":"90d20520d7006fc26338129858206757837b4604","tid":2310280,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0efdd9e3fc46a7d48322169a2b7a4f2da1f14197","tid":2310280,"uid":55913,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T08:07:37.000Z","msg":"夠打既一早打左搶埋啦洗撚咀炮咩<br />\n你睇香港又打又殺幾威威"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T08:35:21.000Z","msg":"最驚支那間諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bbf24ba8e3bcfe33a524241cb6650ffc1254f5b","tid":2310280,"uid":264326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0efdd9e3fc46a7d48322169a2b7a4f2da1f14197","tid":2310280,"uid":55913,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T08:07:37.000Z","msg":"夠打既一早打左搶埋啦洗撚咀炮咩<br />\n你睇香港又打又殺幾威威"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T08:38:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地又輸啦經理"},{"pid":"dccfee8e5adf373a5beea00a2e