moji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家現役嗰兩架海獅級仲係二戰時期落水 作戰能力基本上係.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家起緊嗰隻劍龍級起碼要2024先落水，分分鐘2026先服役<br />\n<br />\n如果要成支潛艇艦隊服役起碼2030年打後<br />\n但係當台灣起緊潛艇嘅同時支共都做緊一樣嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n正所謂 一年陸軍 十年空軍 百年海軍<br />\n要建立一支海軍唔係想像之中咁容易<br />\n<br />\n支共都用咗50幾年先有半隻腳由綠水海軍踩入藍水海軍<br />\n<br />\n不過我諗支共海軍同海上自衛隊打嘅話應該都係平手，只要日本肯幫台灣協防嘅話中國喺水面作戰嗰方面唔會有明顯優勢"},{"pid":"72b215876bda3d9a832d4d2eeb485ebedd1149a0","tid":2310280,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T12:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b5fc2b5aa5604ccf2fcde41813c46781724e10a","tid":2310280,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb7030dcf76acd62525ba20d156bcdafd7e27800","tid":2310280,"uid":107656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T09:13:45.000Z","msg":"報導曬出黎<br />\n仲叫唔叫伏擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T13:04:28.000Z","msg":"北部伏擊區既水深 係極深<br />\n潛左入去 真係好難搵得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c56acdc82437bea576f876030a0947bb4c3d85f","tid":2310280,"uid":337119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T16:33:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}